RH = '''One of the major houses of the Sirius sector, ruled by the Kaiser. Rheinland is the stronghold of the German nation, possessing phenomenally developed heavy industry and a significant military fleet.'''
RC = '''"Daumann" controls the main production facilities in Rheinland territory. The corporation's headquarters is in the Stuttgart system and produces the highest quality industrial goods and the most durable components for the production of ships and stations, as well as components for repairing mining vessels.'''
R_TR = '''The "Interspace" trading corporation relocated to Rheinland after the bankruptcy of Republican Shipping. This organization now handles the majority of trade shipments within Rheinland and delivers goods to any point in Sirius.'''
R_BH = '''The private military company "Asgard" consists of motivated ex-military personnel working to support Rheinland's police forces. "Asgard" conducts the largest number of operations in the border systems; the PMC's headquarters is located at the Potsdam station in the Berlin system.'''
R_PI = '''The "Bundschuh" movement, also known as the "Peasant's Shoe", consists of impoverished Rheinland peasants and farmers, whose poverty stems from sharply increased taxes within Rheinland.'''
RX = '''The "Hessians" are former mercenaries who were previously hired by other houses to participate in their conflicts for money. The Hessians were particularly active in the Munich Conflict with Kusari. After losing funding from the Rheinland government, as well as the absence of contracts from other governments, the Hessians began seeking less legal ways to earn money and are now engaged in terrorist activities in Rheinland.'''
JUNK = '''Junkers are petty bandits whose goal is to dismantle ship wreckage for spare parts. In addition, they engage in smuggling and are generally quite dangerous individuals, as when they have a clear advantage, they can attack straggling convoys or simply lone pilots.'''

LI = '''The Republic of Liberty is the wealthiest and most influential nation in the Sirius sector. Populated by people of American descent, Liberty is the main center of trade and the development of transport technologies.'''
LC = '''The "DeepSpace" corporation is engaged in the development and production of modern transport systems within Liberty territory. "DeepSpace" develops the most advanced technologies in the field of maintaining trade lanes, jump gates, and other means of transportation.'''
L_TR = '''"Ageria" is engaged not only in maintaining trade lanes, jump gates, and all transport arteries of Sirius, but also in the delivery of practically all popular goods. This organization rightfully leads in delivery speed, which has earned it the title of the main pride and technological advantage of the House of Liberty.'''
L_BH = '''The private military company "Shield" was created as an alternative monitoring and security service in Liberty. The peak of this organization's development coincided with the end of the civil war with the Confederate separatists. "Shield" PMC states its main task as countering underground separatist cells, usually solving its tasks through preemptive strikes.'''
L_PI = '''An organization seeking to change the form of government in Liberty from republican to confederate. It was largely suppressed during a local civil war; it is currently underground and carries out terrorist attacks throughout Liberty territory.'''
LX = '''A gang of bandits tracing its origins to antisocial elements from the planet Manhattan. Engages in robbery and smuggling within Liberty territory.'''
ASF = '''The Alliance Security Service is a more powerful version of the Liberty Security Force. At one time, this organization had offices in all Sirius houses, but currently operates primarily in Liberty and Bretonia.'''
SL = '''The "Starline" gang is a former legal private military company which, although formally classified as bandits, quite officially receives funding from the Liberty government to maintain stability in the Minor Omicron system and adjacent systems.'''
HACK = '''A group of bandits specializing in targeted attacks on trade lanes within Liberty territory. The origin of this group is unknown, but it is theorized to have formed from petty thieves in the Columbia system.'''

BR = '''The Kingdom of Bretonia is ruled by Her Majesty Queen Carina. Bretonians are a house populated predominantly by Franco-English settlers, but they consider British traditions to be the basis of their culture. The Kingdom is a leader in the energy sector in Sirius, thus considered the most energy-independent house.'''
BC = '''The royal enterprise "BMM" is the main producer of energy equipment and radioactive fuel within Bretonia territory, and also supplies its products to nearby territories. In addition, the corporation produces a complete set of spare parts for reactors, power plants, and other energy components of ships and stations.'''
B_TR = '''The corporation "Bowex" (short for "Border World Export") is engaged in cargo delivery throughout Sirius and primarily works on delivering thoraxes produced in Bretonia.'''
B_BH = '''The private military company "Royal-Force" is an officially affiliated organization in the service of the Queen of Bretonia, which ensures the operation of border colonies, as well as the control and protection of territories adjacent to the Ulster system.'''
B_PI = '''The "Gaian" represent an organization opposing dangerous energy and terraforming developments within Bretonia. Unfortunately, having exhausted legal methods, this organization currently uses only terrorist ones.'''
BX = '''The Irish Republican Army is an evolution of the ideas of the "Molly" bandits who previously existed in Bretonia territory. The IRA is more focused on the goal of separating Irish territories from the House of Bretonia and considers its main task to be the defense of its main base—the Ulster system—from Bretonian encroachment.'''
XENOS = '''The Xenos are maximally hostile to all factions in Sirius and are one of the most secretive organizations.'''

KU = '''The House of Kusari is ruled by a military leader—the Shogun—who holds under his authority prefectures predominantly populated by Japanese people. Kusari differs from other houses in its particular loyalty to the leader and nobility, and its local industrialists are leaders in the production of electronics and other high-tech devices.'''
KC = '''The "Kishiro" corporation is engaged in the mining of gold and silver ore, as well as the production of a huge range of electronic products within Kusari territory. This is the most advanced and technological product, renowned for its reliability, quality, and valued throughout the Sirius sector.'''
K_TR = '''The "Samura" corporation is considered the main artery of the Kusari economy and is engaged in the delivery of all possible cargo both within the Shogunate and to nearby systems.'''
K_BH = '''The private military company "Black Dragon" consists of former representatives of the "Blood Dragon" organization. The former Blood Dragons helped overthrow the weak government and strengthen the Shogun's power, for which they received a special position in the hierarchy and the title of samurai. Currently, they continue to serve the Shogun and ensure the stability of Kusari's borders from any encroachment.'''
K_PI = '''The "Golden Chrysanthemums" consider their main task to be changing the form of power in Kusari to a matriarchy. Despite such a feminist orientation, this organization has received support even among the poor male population of Kusari.'''
KX = '''The "Shinobi" clan is a mysterious organization of killers and assassins who have no restrictions on the use of force; their target can be any person depending on the job's price. But since contracts are not infinite, the Shinobi often go on independent raids and terrorize the lawful forces of Kusari.'''
FARM = '''The Farmers Alliance consists of bankrupt farmers from the planet Kyushu, who were particularly affected by the loss of agricultural land volume on the planet and the development of synthetic food production.'''

CO = '''The Spanish Corsairs are representatives of the lost House of Spain and are currently engaged in terrorist activity in Sirius. Their main goal is considered to be access to resources and interception of goods to ensure their survival in the Outer Worlds.'''
OUT = '''The Spanish Outcasts are former neighbors of the Corsairs. After the rise of the Order, the Outcasts even had the opportunity to establish an alliance with the Corsairs, which soon ended, leading to a significant migration of Outcasts from Corsair territories. Currently, Outcasts can be found in almost all territories of Sirius. They usually lead a hermitic and solitary life, but sometimes also enter into armed conflicts with civilians.'''
OR = '''The New Order is a remnant of the great organization that provided Sirius with protection from the Nomad invasion. Currently, the Order continues to work on protecting Sirius from the alien threat, but its influence is felt more in the Outer Worlds, where this organization has become the main means of ensuring the standard of living among the Spanish population.'''